The local-bench source code (the cli/ runner and the web/ site) is licensed
under the Apache License, Version 2.0 — see the top-level LICENSE file.

This project includes frozen benchmark item sets derived from third-party
datasets, and adapts third-party verifier code. Each upstream carries its own
license, which continues to apply in full. Full third-party license texts are
in the LICENSES/ directory; a per-dataset redistribution analysis is in
docs/foundations/license-inventory-v1.md. Upstream licenses below were
verified against the upstream Hugging Face card / repository on 2026-07-04,
and re-verified 2026-07-19 (dataset licensing review; scratchpad/
dataset-licensing-review-2026-07-19.md) unless noted.


